OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few showers
OL,7,Fpossible, dry with clear spells
OL,8,Fhowever over Moray. Remaining cloudy
OL,9,Fovernight with showers possible for
OL,10,Fall parts. Light northwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy and overcast day with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of showery rain spreading
OL,14,Fsouthwards. Showers may become heavy
OL,15,Fat times in the afternoon in the west.
OL,16,FDrier in the east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
